|WKBSYNTAX
==========|YKB

wimpy # 

|YKOWhere # is equal to the percentage of remaining HP you want to run at

|WKBDESCRIPTION
===========|YKO

Toggle wimpy mode. If you are in wimpy mode, your legs will run away
if your hit points goes below whatever percent of your HP you have
designated.

Default for a new player is brave mode. You will not run away.

This is no secure thing. It might save you, however some monsters hack away 
more than your allowed % of your HP, and you might find yourself dead 
without warning. Also, some monsters can run as fast as your legs.
